title: Ordinary Differential Equations - Richard K. Miller
description:
Ordinary Differential Equations - Richard K. Miller, Anthony N. Michel (Academic Press, 1982).pdf

Acclaimed by IEEE Control Systems Magazine as a welcome addition to books in the field, this self-contained treatment is appropriate for courses in nonlinear system analysis. Geared toward advanced undergraduates and graduate students in mathematics, engineering, and the sciences, its highlight is a scholarly treatment of the stability of dynamical systems
